        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-22 09:13:12.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nIs there a ONAP wide recommendation on which version of Alpine Linux to use? Seems like a few different versions are being used in different projects.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "17b0866bce50bb737acfeaf495f4b540f9decf92",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2477,
          "name": "Takamune Cho",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "takamune.cho@att.com",
          "username": "Takamune_Cho"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-22 13:40:23.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nhttps://wiki.onap.org/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=45293323 there is a pdf called: Dublin-Footprint-Optimizations.pdf. the Alpine linux dist is a light weight linux dist version. for CDT, we only reduced like 10MB, but other containers reduced size largely.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "68c4799ba00b5491cb4845d54eb266b3c4efdb99",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 3979,
          "name": "Joss Armstrong",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "joss.armstrong@ericsson.com",
          "username": "jarmstrong001"
        },
        "author_role": "REVIEWER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-22 14:14:37.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nYes, I understand the migration to Alpine to reduce footprint. My question is only on the specific version we use as I notice that other projects are using different versions of Alpine. e.g. CCSDK seems to be migrating to version 3.7 https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/74678/3/alpine/src/main/docker/Dockerfile",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
      {
        "id": "9e818d2fc789c2c59ff7ac941bc56473abd3dee7",
        "author": {
          "account_id": 2477,
          "name": "Takamune Cho",
          "display_name": null,
          "email": "takamune.cho@att.com",
          "username": "Takamune_Cho"
        },
        "author_role": "OWNER",
        "timestamp": "2019-01-22 15:04:07.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nthe httpd container is using alpine 3.8 \nhttps://github.com/docker-library/httpd/blob/5a6a1d99f1d6e754ecfcdd7a13e12980b86d7b75/2.4/alpine/Dockerfile\n\nI do not know the difference between alpine 3.7 and 3.8. we can ask Dan.",
        "patchset_number": 1
      },
